- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The proposed approach involves transforming a Lidar point cloud into a depth image and applying image processing techniques such as smoothing and connected component analysis. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): Although the paper does not explicitly mention the use of machine learning, it is possible that some of the image processing techniques involve learning-based methods. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): Similar to the previous point, the paper may involve AI techniques for processing the Lidar point cloud data. 
- cs.GR (Graphics): The paper involves processing 3D point cloud data and generating depth and range angle images, which falls under the domain of computer graphics.
